  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Supplementary Payments</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loioe217da531198434de10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Supplementary Payments</h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> Initially, only a certain percentage of the nominal amount is paid for partially-paid stocks (not listed). To do this, choose condition type supplementary payment, which corrects the initial amount paid by means of a supplementary payment.\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Procedure\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Procedure</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> The supplementary payments condition consists of a due date and a supplementary payment amount.\n</p>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Enter the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Due date</span> of the supplementary payment\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Enter the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Amount</span> or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Percentage rate</span> of the supplementary payment. If you enter a percentage rate the system can calculate the amount automatically, and vice versa.\n</p></li></ol>\n<aside class=\"note\" aria-labelledby=\"n0t\"><div class=\"title\" id=\"n0t\"><strong>Note</strong></div>\n<p class=\"p\">\n</p><p class=\"p\">The pay-in rate and the total supplementary payments must not exceed 100%.\n</p></aside>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}